{"data":[{"name":"1:1","price":"慈悲あまねく*慈愛深き*アッラー*の御名において。","arabic":"بِسۡمِ ٱللَّهِ ٱلرَّحۡمَٰنِ ٱلرَّحِيمِ","category":["1 (Al-Fatihah)","Al-Fatihah","Surah Al-Fatihah"],"ayahNumber":1,"juzNumber":1,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"bis'mi al-lahi al-raḥmāni al-raḥīmi ","translations":["In (the) name","(of) Allah","the Most Gracious","the Most Merciful","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["bis'mi","al-lahi","al-raḥmāni","al-raḥīmi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,580],[2,580,1409],[3,1409,2502],[4,2502,5840]]}},{"name":"1:2","price":"全創造物の主*、アッラー*に称賛*あれ、","arabic":"ٱلۡحَمۡدُ لِلَّهِ رَبِّ ٱلۡعَٰلَمِينَ","category":["1 (Al-Fatihah)","Al-Fatihah","Surah Al-Fatihah"],"ayahNumber":2,"juzNumber":1,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"al-ḥamdu lillahi rabbi al-ʿālamīna ","translations":["All praises and thanks","(be) to Allah","the Lord","of the universe","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["al-ḥamdu","lillahi","rabbi","al-ʿālamīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1000],[2,1000,1860],[3,1860,2490],[4,2490,5525]]}},{"name":"1:3","price":"慈悲あまねく慈愛深きお方、","arabic":"ٱلرَّحۡمَٰنِ ٱلرَّحِيمِ","category":["1 (Al-Fatihah)","Al-Fatihah","Surah Al-Fatihah"],"ayahNumber":3,"juzNumber":1,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"al-raḥmāni al-raḥīmi ","translations":["The Most Gracious","the Most Merciful","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["al-raḥmāni","al-raḥīmi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1240],[3,1240,4565]]}},{"name":"1:4","price":"報いの日*の支配者（に）。","arabic":"مَٰلِكِ يَوۡمِ ٱلدِّينِ","category":["1 (Al-Fatihah)","Al-Fatihah","Surah Al-Fatihah"],"ayahNumber":4,"juzNumber":1,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"māliki yawmi al-dīni ","translations":["(The) Master","(of the) Day","(of the) Judgment","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["māliki","yawmi","al-dīni",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,820],[2,820,1420],[3,1420,4585]]}},{"name":"1:5","price":"私たちはあなただけを崇拝*し，あなただけにお力添えを乞います¹。","arabic":"إِيَّاكَ نَعۡبُدُ وَإِيَّاكَ نَسۡتَعِينُ","category":["1 (Al-Fatihah)","Al-Fatihah","Surah Al-Fatihah"],"ayahNumber":5,"juzNumber":1,"footnotes":"１　「崇拝*」だけでなく、アッラー*のお力添えがなければ何事も叶わない。イブン・カスィール*は「（このアーヤ*の）前半部分では、アッラー*に何か他のものを並べることとの決別が、そして後半部分では、自らに何らかの力が備わっているとすることの決別と、アッラー*のみに全てを委ねることが命じられている」とし、この意味こそが「開端章はクルアーン*の奥義（おうぎ）であり、開端章の奥義がこのアーヤ*である」という先人たちの言葉の所以（ゆえん）であるとしている（1：70参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"iyyāka naʿbudu wa-iyyāka nastaʿīnu ","translations":["You Alone","we worship","and You Alone","we ask for help","(5)"],"transliterationArr":["iyyāka","naʿbudu","wa-iyyāka","nastaʿīnu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,990],[2,990,1760],[3,1760,2880],[4,2880,6635]]}},{"name":"1:6","price":"私たちを、まっすぐな道¹へとお導きください。","arabic":"ٱهۡدِنَا ٱلصِّرَٰطَ ٱلۡمُسۡتَقِيمَ","category":["1 (Al-Fatihah)","Al-Fatihah","Surah Al-Fatihah"],"ayahNumber":6,"juzNumber":1,"footnotes":"１　来世での成功へと続く道である、イスラーム*のこと（ムヤッサル1頁参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"ih'dinā al-ṣirāṭa al-mus'taqīma ","translations":["Guide us","(to) the path","the straight","(6)"],"transliterationArr":["ih'dinā","al-ṣirāṭa","al-mus'taqīma",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,740],[2,740,1640],[3,1640,5525]]}},{"name":"1:7","price":"あなたが恩恵をお授けになった者たち¹、つまり、（あなたの）お怒りを受けるでもなく、迷うでもない者たち²の道へ。³","arabic":"صِرَٰطَ ٱلَّذِينَ أَنۡعَمۡتَ عَلَيۡهِمۡ غَيۡرِ ٱلۡمَغۡضُوبِ عَلَيۡهِمۡ وَلَا ٱلضَّآلِّينَ","category":["1 (Al-Fatihah)","Al-Fatihah","Surah Al-Fatihah"],"ayahNumber":7,"juzNumber":1,"footnotes":"１　婦人章66-69も参照。 ２　「お怒りを受ける」者たちとは、知識を預かってはいても、それに沿って行わなかった当時のユダヤ教徒*、および彼らと同様の状態にある者たちのこと。また「迷う」者たちとは、無知ゆえに導かれず、正しい道から迷い去ってしまった当時のキリスト教徒*、および彼らと同様の状態にある者たちのこと（前掲書、同頁参照）。 ３ 礼拝中かどうかに関わらず、開端章を読み終えた後には、「アーミーン（アッラーよ、聞き届けたまえ）」と唱えることが薦（すす）められている（前掲書、同頁参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"ṣirāṭa alladhīna anʿamta ʿalayhim ghayri al-maghḍūbi ʿalayhim walā al-ḍālīna ","translations":["(The) path","(of) those","You have bestowed (Your) Favors","on them","not (of)","those who earned (Your) wrath","on themselves","and not","(of) those who go astray","(7)"],"transliterationArr":["ṣirāṭa","alladhīna","anʿamta","ʿalayhim","ghayri","al-maghḍūbi","ʿalayhim","walā","al-ḍālīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,750],[2,750,1670],[3,1670,2690],[4,2690,3620],[5,3620,4210],[6,4210,5380],[7,5380,6380],[8,6380,6670],[9,6670,13175]]}}],"chapter":["1 (Al-Fatihah)","Al-Fatihah","Surah Al-Fatihah","Chapter Al-Fatihah","Fatihah","Surah Fatihah","Chapter Fatihah","Al Fatihah","Surah Al Fatihah","Chapter Al Fatihah","Surah 1","Chapter 1","The Opening","الفَاتِحَة"],"version":{"key":"japanese_saeedsato","direction":"ltr","language_iso_code":"ja","version":"1.0.10","last_update":1709035504,"title":"Japanese translation - Saeed Sato","description":"Translation of the Quran meanings into Japanese by Saeed Sato. printed in 1440 H."}}